main event: Several unidentified objects were observed by military personnel at Davidsonthian AFB in Arizona.
interesting points: The objects were described as metallic in nature and traveling at an extremely high rate of speed in an erratic, pendulous course.
The objects were observed to be traveling in a vertical plane at a high angle of elevation, approximately 45 to 65 degrees above the horizon.
The objects were observed to increase their speed and angle of elevation.
Two jet aircraft were also tracked by radar for approximately 25 minutes, moving rapidly in a weaving fashion at around 600 knots, but their identity was not established.
A diagram was included showing the movement of two objects relative to the sun.
sighted object: metallic objects traveling at high speeds in an erratic pattern
